Thegither is an app for connecting people up.

You can use Thegither, for example, to set up a jobs board, lost-and-found, rideshare, online swap meet, volunteer opportunities, dating site, or use your imagination.  Users advertise something they have ("We're hiring", "I found") or something they want ("I'm available", "I lost").  Responses can be seen only by the original poster.  Users must be signed on to a Google account to use the application.

Thegither is a Google AppEngine application writtin in Python.  Thegither uses the GAE datastore to store data, and the GAE user library to manage accounts.
